text: If you believe you have discovered a vulnerability or have a security incident to report, please email

Please use this contact information for all IT Security matters to ensure they are captured correctly and handled in a timely manner. We consider all reports our highest priority and we will work to address any reported issue as quickly as possible. Please be sure to include a detailed summary of the issue and your contact information.

If you’ve discovered a security concern, we’ll work with you to make sure that we understand the scope of the issue and that we fully address the exposure. When given sufficient notification, we'll do our best to work with any responsible party alerting us to a security issue, we'll assign resources to swiftly investigate the issue and engage a response team appropriate to the severity of the issue.
